en16931

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • en16931.Entity

  • public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents an Entity. It can either play the role of seller (AccountingSupplierParty) or buyer (AccountingCustomerParty) in a transaction described by an Invoice.
